        "rdfs:label": "battery chemistry",
        "rdfs:comment": {
            "@value": "<div>Composition of a product in general terms by specifying the cathode and anode\nactive material as well as electrolyte.\nDIN DKE Spec 99100 chapter reference: 6.5.2</div>",
