        "rdfs:comment": {
            "@value": "<div>Component materials used: Naming the materials (as a composition of substances)\nin cathode, anode, electrolyte according to public standards.\nDIN DKE Spec 99100 chapter reference: 6.5.3-6.5.4</div>",
